Unnamed Thermal Hotspot Tracking Program

All versions released before 2020-01-01 are tested and built on an unknown
release of OpenCV2, presumably somewhere in the 2.4 range.

All versions released after 2020-01-01 are tested and build on OpenCV
version 4.2.0.

